snippet.title: Lesson 49 - What is Enterprise Architecture?
snippet.description: Ask 10 people what enterprise architecture is and you will get 10 different answers. In this lesson Mark Richards provides a definition and context of what Enterprise Architecture is and sets the stage for further lessons about enterprise architecture. Stay tuned each Monday for more lessons in Software Architecture at https://www.developertoarchitect.com/lessons/.
